citHeader("To cite holcmapr in publications use citations for package and Mapping Inequality. Additionally, if using population-weighted centroid-based methods, please cite, US Census Centers of Population. Additionally, if using life expectancy results, please cite USALEEP. Additionally, if using mental or physical health results, please cite CDC PLACES. Citations for these references appear below.")

